<HEADLINE> Tonga King Leaves Shanghai for Xiamen </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, October 14 (Xinhua)-- Taufa'ahau Tupou IV, the King
of Tonga, left Shanghai this morning for Xiamen, a major port city
in east China's Fujian Province, to continue his state visit to
China.
</P>
