<P>
Hangzhou: min. 20 degrees C., max. 26 degrees C., overcast to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Taipei: min. 24 degrees C., max. 29 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Guangzhou: min. 24 degrees C., max. 32 degrees C., drizzle to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong: min. 25 degrees C., max. 30 degrees C., drizzle to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
