address the crisis, especially to halt price hikes, to restore the
availability and affordability of foodstuffs and other basic
commodities, to carry out the Social Net program, to develop the
people's economy and to restructure the banking sector and the
private debts.
</P>
<P>
In the political field, the government took immediate action to
renew the existing legislation in order to allow the holding of a
general election ensuring the election of the people's
representatives.
</P>
<P>
"This is what I can present in the context of carrying out a
comprehensive reform during approximately 512 days or 12,021
hours. As a simple human being, I am fully aware that the whole of
the crisis as an accumulation of problems and disorders that
lasted for quite some time would have been impossible to overcome
in a very short time," he said.
</P>
