<DOCNO> XIE19991015.0341 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-15 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Albright Expresses Condolence to Nyerere's Death </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, October 14 (Xinhua) -- U.S. Secretary of State
Madeleine Albright Thursday expressed sadness over the death of
former Tanzanian President Julius Nyerere, calling him a "giant on
the world stage."
</P>
<P>
She said in a statement that Nyerere as the first president of
Tanzania had laid the foundation for over 30 years of peace and
stability in his country.
</P>
<P>
"His belief in the need to provide security for all people of
his country guided his unique vision of the social compact," she
said. 
</P>
