Irrigation System in northwest China's Ningxia Province aiming to
support the poor.
</P>
<P>
Started in 1996, the project is designed to lift 800 million
cubic meters of water from the Yellow River to hundreds of meters
high to irrigate 133,000 hectares of barren land to help solve the
food and clothing problem of 1 million people in the area.
</P>
