<HEADLINE> NBA Lakers Star Bryant Breaks Hand </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, October 14 (Xinhua) -- NBA Los Angeles Lakers All-
Star guard Kobe Bryant has a fracture bone in his right hand and
will be sidelined for a minimum of six weeks.
