<HEADLINE> ASEM Science Ministers Meeting Concludes in Beijing (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The meeting will play a guiding role in Asia-Europe scientific
and technological collaboration in the future, Zhu said.
</P>
<P>
Assessing the fruits of the meeting, the Chinese minister noted
that the successful convening of the meeting itself represents a
big achievement.
</P>
<P>
Though today's telecommunications technologies are quite
advanced, it is still very useful that the ministers meet face-to-
face to discuss social and economic issues of common interest, Zhu
said.
</P>
<P>
The first ASEM Science and Technology Meeting, with the theme "
Science and Technology Cooperation in the 21st Century," will help
to propel the economic prosperity and mutual development of the
two continents, Zhu said.
</P>
